Package Game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Animal
    parent Class for farm animals which are stored in the farm class.
    AnimalItem
    item class for animals items are consumed by animals to increase happiness or health levels
    Chicken
    calls the super() constructor of the animal superclass with default attributes of the chicken class
    Cow
    calls the super() constructor of the animal superclass with default attributes of the cow class
    Crop
    the Crop class defines each crop the player may grow or purchase from the shop, each with different attributes which are set upon construction based on the string type
    CropItem
    item class for crop objects that are consumed to promote crop growth
    Farm
    farm class is the environment the player plays in.
    Farmer
    The Farmer class is the character played by the user they may set a name and an age for this character.
    FarmSetupWindow
    gui screen for farm setup window
    GameWindow
    The main GUI for the game used to view animals, crops , items, do actions and view the marketplace
    Main
    the main game engine that runs the whole game by tying all classes together.
    MarketWindow
    gui screen for the shop screen
    Pig
    calls the super() constructor of the animal super class with associated attributes of the pig class.
